---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Privacy Policy - Accountability Bet</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 font-sans">
		<!-- Header -->
		<header class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4">
				<a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-600">Accountability Bet</a>
			</div>
		</header>

		<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

			<div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8">
				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						Accountability Bet ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and website (collectively, the "Service").
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
						We are based in Switzerland and comply with Swiss data protection laws (FADP) and the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) where applicable.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">Personal Information</h3>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
						<li>Email address (for account creation and notifications)</li>
						<li>Display name (chosen by you)</li>
						<li>Profile photo (optional)</li>
					</ul>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">Usage Data</h3>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
						<li>Bet details you create (goals, stakes, duration)</li>
						<li>Proof photos you upload</li>
						<li>Messages exchanged with accountability partners</li>
						<li>App usage statistics (anonymized)</li>
					</ul>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">Technical Data</h3>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
						<li>Device type and operating system</li>
						<li>IP address (for security purposes)</li>
						<li>Browser type (for web access)</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
						<li>To provide and maintain the Service</li>
						<li>To send you notifications about your bets and proofs</li>
						<li>To enable communication with your accountability partners</li>
						<li>To calculate and track IOUs</li>
						<li>To improve and optimize the Service</li>
						<li>To respond to your support requests</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Data Sharing</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data to third parties.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
						Your data is shared only with:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-2">
						<li><strong>Your accountability partners:</strong> They can see your bet details, proof photos, and progress for bets you share with them.</li>
						<li><strong>Service providers:</strong> We use Supabase (database hosting in Switzerland), Resend (email delivery), and Vercel (web hosting) to operate the Service.</li>
						<li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> We may disclose data if required by law.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Data Storage & Security</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						Your data is stored on servers located in Switzerland and/or the European Union. We use industry-standard encryption (TLS/SSL) for data in transit and encryption at rest for sensitive data.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
						Proof photos are stored securely and are only accessible to you and your designated accountability partner.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						Under GDPR and Swiss law, you have the right to:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-2">
						<li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
						<li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate data</li>
						<li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
						<li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured format</li>
						<li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to certain processing activities</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
						To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@accountabilitybet.ch" class="text-purple-600 hover:underline">privacy@accountabilitybet.ch</a>.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Data Retention</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We retain your data for as long as your account is active. If you delete your account, we will delete your personal data within 30 days, except where we are required to retain it for legal purposes.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
						Proof photos are deleted 90 days after a bet is completed.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Cookies</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We use essential cookies to keep you logged in and maintain your session. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
						We may use anonymous analytics to understand how the Service is used. This data cannot be used to identify you personally.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						The Service is not intended for users under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from children.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by email or through the Service.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
						<strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@accountabilitybet.ch" class="text-purple-600 hover:underline">privacy@accountabilitybet.ch</a><br/>
						<strong>Address:</strong> [Company Address, Switzerland]
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</main>

		<!-- Footer -->
		<footer class="bg-gray-100 border-t border-gray-200 py-8 mt-12">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-gray-600 text-sm">
				<p>&copy; 2026 Accountability Bet. Made in Switzerland ðŸ‡¨ðŸ‡­</p>
				<div class="mt-4 space-x-4">
					<a href="/" class="hover:text-gray-900">Home</a>
					<a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</a>
					<a href="/terms" class="hover:text-gray-900">Terms of Service</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>

		<style>
			body {
				font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
